summary: Mcu idea: Avengers teaching other Avengers hero stuff
body:
Mcu idea: Avengers teaching other Avengers hero stuff

Natasha training Parker in more advanced combat. Him asking ‘is this gonna kill the guy? Cause I don’t want that.’ Natasha replies, ‘Okay, we’ll skip that move then.’

Dr Strange introducing Rhodes to meditation and other magic stuff. A year later he doesn’t need Tony’s exoskeleton to walk.

Sam and Thor sky racing to see how to improve one another’s flying.

T’Challa & Shuri on the Sheild hellicarrier for 12 minuets and giving Nick a list of problems/improvements before talking about movies.

Scott & Clint just…hanging out being dads as their kids play.

The Guardians taking Steve, Tony, Parker & Shuri to other planets. Captain & Ironman are being professional while the teens are just
